mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: "Hot Line-Late News", "As I See It", "The Plus Ten Mini Handbook", "New Approach to Dropouts", "Take a Good Look", "The Dancers Walkthru", "Square Dance Diary", "Roundancer Module", "Paging the Round Dancers: Bill and Ruth Winkler", "Smoother Dancing Poster", "Traveling Callers Directory", "Ladies on the Square", "Style Lab-Substitute and Zoom", "National Square Dance Convention", "Round the World of Square Dancing", "Callers/Teachers Workshop", "Caller of the Month: Archie Howell", "Spotlight a Dancer: Dan and Pauline Sakahara", "Square Dance Date Book", "On the Record: Reviews", and "Fashion Feature".
